&lt;h1&gt;Workflow Platform Integration Specialist&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Overview:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for an experienced and motivated &lt;strong&gt;Software Engineer&lt;/strong&gt; to join our startup team, dedicated to expanding the capabilities of our workflow platform through various integrations. The primary focus of this role is to enhance our platform&#39;s functionality by seamlessly integrating it with external systems and services. As a &lt;strong&gt;Software Engineer&lt;/strong&gt; specializing in workflow platform integrations, you will play a crucial role in shaping the future of our product.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You Should Have:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Experience&lt;/strong&gt;: 3-5 years of hands-on experience working with complex and distributed software applications.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Development Skills&lt;/strong&gt;: Proficiency in developing applications from scratch, demonstrating your ability to build robust and scalable solutions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Java Expertise&lt;/strong&gt;: Strong expertise in &lt;strong&gt;Java&lt;/strong&gt;, &lt;strong&gt;Spring Boot&lt;/strong&gt;, and &lt;strong&gt;Hibernate&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Database Fundamentals&lt;/strong&gt;: Solid understanding of database fundamentals, including &lt;strong&gt;caching&lt;/strong&gt;, &lt;strong&gt;query optimization&lt;/strong&gt;, and &lt;strong&gt;indexing&lt;/strong&gt;, with a preference for experience with &lt;strong&gt;PostgreSQL&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
